strings.Value: "Ughhh, I didn't like that masked witch. Who are these Defaced Sisters, anyway? Why would fierce warriors crawl through dungeons on their say, instead of fighting and hunting?"
"I've never heard of them before either. Perhaps they're some new religious order? It is indeed strange that the barbarians would obey them."
"She gave the feeling of something... familiar to me. Grief, and darkness."
"One thing is sure. They did not tell us all they know."
"I feel the Defaced Sisters share some terrible grief. What could make these women reject their names and their faces?"
